definitions.definition: umpteen, tens of, dozens of (an unspecified number, usually between 10 and 100)

parsedExamples.example: Der Verkäufer hat mir zig verschiedene Modelle gezeigt.
parsedExamples.translation: The salesperson showed me umpteen different models.
